text:
When I smell something new, I try and find
  out what the odor is coming from.
I like to discover new places to go.

If I hear something rustling in the grass I
  have to see what it is.

I like visiting art galleries and art
  museums.

When I see a new fabric, I like to touch and
  feel it.

I like to listen to new and unusual kinds of
  music.

When I hear a musical instrument and I am
  not sure what it is, I like to see it.

I enjoy trying different kinds of ethnic
  foods.

When I hear a strange sound, I usually try
  to find out what caused it.
